(4, 1, 'Samsung LN46B750 46-Inch 1080p 240 Hz LCD HDTV', 'Thereâ€™s no reason to settle for less than picture perfect. With this LCD HDTV youâ€™ll get amazing picture quality with 1080p resolution and a 150,000:1 dynamic contrast ratio. Plus Auto Motion Plus 240Hzâ„¢ delivers action scenes that are more realistic than ever before. And Medi@2.0â„¢ gives you more than TV programming and movies. Now you can access content from Yahoo!Â® and FlickrÂ®. Turn your high-definition dreams into reality with the LN46B750 HDTV.', 0, 'Samsung_LN46B750_46-Inch_1080p_240_Hz_LCD_HDTV', 'Samsung LN46B750 46-Inch 1080p 240 Hz LCD HDTV', 'Thereâ€™s no reason to settle for less than picture perfect. With this LCD HDTV youâ€™ll get amazing pic', 'Samsung LN46B750 46-Inch 1080p 240 Hz LCD HDTV', 'Thereâ€™s no reason to settle for less than picture perfect. With this LCD HDTV youâ€™ll get amazing picture quality with 1080p resolution and a 150,000:1 dynamic contrast ratio. Plus Auto Motion Plus 240Hzâ„¢ delivers action scenes that are more realistic than ever before. And Medi@2.0â„¢ gives you more than TV programming and movies. Now you can access content from Yahoo!Â® and FlickrÂ®. Turn your high-definition dreams into reality with the LN46B750 HDTV.'),
(5, 1, 'Samsung  LN32B550 32-inch 1080p LCD HDTV', 'Does your existing TV have sharp, crystal-clear images and brilliant color? This SAMSUNG LCD TV doesâ”€ along with a 70,000:1 dynamic contrast ratio that contributes to superior picture quality. It also has a beautiful crystal-clear neck and Touch of Colorâ„¢ bezel design. Plus four HDMI connections make it easy and convenient to hook up digital devices, and the USB 2.0 port lets you play a slideshow of your favorite photos from a thumb drive. With a TV like the LN32B550 thereâ€™s no need to settle for anything thatâ€™s less than amazing.', 2, 'Samsung__LN32B550_32_1080p_LCD_HDTV', 'Samsung  LN32B550 32 1080p LCD HDTV', 'Does your existing TV have sharp, crystal-clear images and brilliant color? This SAMSUNG LCD TV does', 'Samsung  LN32B550 32-inch 1080p LCD HDTV', 'Does your existing TV have sharp, crystal-clear images and brilliant color? This SAMSUNG LCD TV doesâ”€ along with a 70,000:1 dynamic contrast ratio that contributes to superior picture quality. It also has a beautiful crystal-clear neck and Touch of Colorâ„¢ bezel design. Plus four HDMI connections make it easy and convenient to hook up digital devices, and the USB 2.0 port lets you play a slideshow of your favorite photos from a thumb drive. With a TV like the LN32B550 thereâ€™s no need to settle for anything thatâ€™s less than amazing.'),
(6, 1, 'Sony 55-inches Class BRAVIA XBR8 LCD HDTV', '<ul class="disc">\n<li><h5>Changing The Way You See TV</h5>\nBehold breathtaking images that appear to jump off the screen. The XBR8 Series features TRILUMINOS RGB Dynamic LED Backlight technology to deliver more accurate color reproduction and higher purity of colors. Combined with local dimming technology, you''ll notice brighter whites and deeper blacks with astonishing depth and extraordinary shadow detail. \n</li>\n<li>\n<h5>The Ultimate HD Experience</h5>\n\nWith Full HD 1080p resolution panel (1920x1080), this HDTV lets you take full advantage of HD sources such as Blu-ray Disc players and PLAYSTATIONÂ®3 systems that can deliver 1080p content. \n</li>\n<li>\n<h5>Smooth, Fast-Moving Action</h5>\n\nEnjoy a more fluid, natural and realistic viewing experience while watching fast-action sports and movies. Motionflow 120Hz PRO technology enhances sharpness and delivers smooth motion for fast-action pictures. Sequential scanning technology further improves picture clarity by reducing image lag. \n</li>\n<li>\n<h5>Seeing is Believing</h5>\n\nExperience a supremely sharp, crystal clear image from any video resolution with BRAVIA EngineÂ® 2 PRO. It''s Sony''s most advanced video processing system optimizing standard definition and high definition to maximize contrast, color and brightness and motion while reducing noise. \n</li>\n<li>\n<h5>Color Us Green</h5>\nFor more than 10 years, Sony has promoted the use of recycled plastics and has continued to reuse over 16,000 tons of plastic per year since 2006.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5>A Broader Color Spectrum</h5>\nBy combining a 10-bit processor and 10-bit panel, the BRAVIA XBR8 Series is able to display billions of colors. You''ll also notice smoother color transitions and avoid a picture with a "paint by numbers" look.\n</li>\n</ul>', 4, 'Sony_55-inches_Class_BRAVIA_XBR8_LCD_HDTV', 'Sony 55-inches Class BRAVIA XBR8 LCD HDTV', 'Changing The Way You See TV\n\nBehold breathtaking images that appear to jump off the screen. The XBR8', 'Sony 55-inches Class BRAVIA XBR8 LCD HDTV', 'Behold breathtaking images that appear to jump off the screen. The XBR8 Series features TRILUMINOS RGB Dynamic LED Backlight technology to deliver more accurate color reproduction and higher purity of colors. Combined with local dimming technology, you''ll notice brighter whites and deeper blacks with astonishing depth and extraordinary shadow detail. '),
(7, 1, 'Sony 46-inches BRAVIA Z Series LCD HDTV', '<ul class="disc">\n<li><h5>Watch Fast-action at Full Speed</h5>\nYour fast-paced movies, sports and games have never looked clearer thanks to Motionflowâ„¢ 240Hz refresh rate. Our most advanced motion processing technology to date delivers an unbelievably smooth, crisp and fluid picture. \nEndless Entertainment\n</li>\n<li>Enjoy free, premium on-demand entertainmentdirectly to your HDTV. Using your in-home broadband connection and BRAVIA HDTV remote control, you can access online content from an ever-growing list of providers including Amazon Video On Demand, YouTubeâ„¢, Sports Illustrated, Sony Pictures, Sony Music, Slacker and Epicurious.com. \n</li>\n<li>\n<h5>Personalize Your Viewing Experience</h5>\nStay in touch with the world and access the latest news, weather, sports, entertainment and more at the touch of a button with BRAVIA Internet Widgets. These small application widgets are located on TV''s display and can be positioned to your liking.\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5>Incredible Full HD Picture Quality</h5>\nFrom the moment you turn on this XBR9, you''ll notice a sharper, more vibrant picture. With BRAVIA Engineâ„¢ 3 fully digital video processor, this TV produces breathtaking picture quality with reduced visual noise, enhanced color and overall image detail even on 1080p sources such as Blu-ray Discâ„¢ players.\n</li>\n</ul>', 3, 'Sony_46-inches_BRAVIA_Z_Series_LCD_HDTV', 'Sony 46-inches BRAVIA Z Series LCD HDTV', 'Watch Fast-action at Full Speed. Your fast-paced movies, sports and games have never looked clearer.', 'Sony 46-inches BRAVIA Z Series LCD HDTV', 'Incredible Full HD Picture Quality\n<br>\nFrom the moment you turn on this XBR9, you''ll notice a sharper, more vibrant picture. With BRAVIA Engineâ„¢ 3 fully digital video processor, this TV produces breathtaking picture quality with reduced visual noise, enhanced color and overall image detail even on 1080p sources such as Blu-ray Discâ„¢ players.\n'),
