(29, 3, 'Lens Case CL-1120', 'Soft Lens Case - for Nikon Zoom Super Wide Angle AF 17-55mm f/2.8G ED-IF AF-S DX Autofocus Lens (Replacement).\nCompatible with: \nAF-S DX Zoom-NIKKOR 17-55mm f/2.8G IF-ED\nPC-E NIKKOR 24mm f/3.5D ED\nPC-E Micro NIKKOR 85mm f/2.8D\nPC-E Micro NIKKOR 45mm f/2.8D ED', 1, 'Lens_Case_CL-1120', 'Lens Case CL-1120', 'Soft Lens Case - for Nikon Zoom Super Wide Angle AF 17-55mm f/2.8G ED-IF AF-S DX Autofocus Lens (Rep', 'Lens Case CL-1120 undefined', 'Soft Lens Case - for Nikon Zoom Super Wide Angle AF 17-55mm f/2.8G ED-IF AF-S DX Autofocus Lens (Replacement). '),
