(33, 3, 'WG-AS1 Water Guard for D3', 'The WG-AS1 water guard is useful for protecting the camera''s hot shoe contact when the SB-900 is mounted on the D3.\nSB-900 AF Speedlight,D3X, D3,D3S', 0, 'WG-AS1_Water_Guard_for_D3', 'WG-AS1 Water Guard for D3', 'The WG-AS1 water guard is useful for protecting the camera''s hot shoe contact when the SB-900 is mou', 'WG-AS1 Water Guard for D3 undefined', 'The WG-AS1 water guard is useful for protecting the camera''s hot shoe contact when the SB-900 is mounted on the D3.'),
(34, 3, '240GB HD HandycamÂ® Camcorder', 'Shoot like a pro and record your memories directly to a massive 240GB hard disk drive with the HDR-XR520V HandycamÂ® camcorder. This impressive camcorder is capable of recording up to 96 hours of high definition (HD) video in HD LP mode. Equipped with an advanced 1/2.88" Exmor Râ„¢ CMOS sensor, you can capture stunning 1920x1080 HD video and 12.1 megapixel still images. Additionally, a built-in GPS receiver helps you keep track of your current location and even remembers where you shot your videos while the professional-quality Sony G Lens delivers superior optical performance.', 10, '240GB_HD_Handycam_Camcorder', '240GB HD Handycam Camcorder', 'Shoot like a pro and record your memories directly to a massive 240GB hard disk drive with the HDR-X', '240GB HD Handycam Camcorder undefined', 'Shoot like a pro and record your memories directly to a massive 240GB hard disk drive with the HDR-XR520V HandycamÂ® camcorder.'),
(35, 3, 'High Definition Handycam', 'Shoot HD quality video with the HDR-CX100/R HandycamÂ® camcorder. This compact and lightweight Memory Stick Duoâ„¢ media camcorder offers 1920x1080 Full HD video recording and 4.0 megapixel still image capture. Packed with a healthy feature set including a 1/5-inch Exmor CMOS sensor, BIONZâ„¢ image processor, Face Detection, Smile Shutterâ„¢ technology and 8GB of embedded flash memory, its most differentiating characteristic is its ultra-compact design.', 3, 'High_Definition_Handycam', 'High Definition Handycam', 'Shoot HD quality video with the HDR-CX100/R HandycamÂ® camcorder. This compact and lightweight Memory', 'High Definition Handycam undefined', 'Shoot HD quality video with the HDR-CX100/R HandycamÂ® camcorder. This compact and lightweight Memory Stick Duoâ„¢ media camcorder offers 1920x1080 Full HD video recording and 4.0 megapixel still image capture. Packed with a healthy feature set including a 1/5-inch Exmor CMOS sensor, BIONZâ„¢ image processor, Face Detection, Smile Shutterâ„¢ technology and 8GB of embedded flash memory, its most differentiating characteristic is its ultra-compact design.'),
(36, 3, 'Handycam CamcorderHDR-TG5V', 'Capture videos in crystal clear HD with this Handycam camcorder bundle. This money-saving kit includes the HDR-TG5V Handycam camcorder, custom-fitted protective case and a separate accessory pouch to hold the included spare battery and travel charger.', 6, 'Handycam_CamcorderHDR-TG5V', 'Handycam CamcorderHDR-TG5V', 'Capture videos in crystal clear HD with this Handycam camcorder bundle. This money-saving kit includ', 'Handycam CamcorderHDR-TG5V undefined', 'Capture videos in crystal clear HD with this Handycam camcorder bundle. This money-saving kit includes the HDR-TG5V Handycam camcorder, custom-fitted protective case and a separate accessory pouch to hold the included spare battery and travel charger.'),
(37, 3, 'Samsung  HMX-R10', 'This ultra-compact camcorder adds an extra level of comfort to every shot you take. Its ergonomic design makes it easy to grip and hold long enough to catch that special memory in full high definition. And the 2.7" touch screen gives you a great view to make sure itâ€™s all captured. Forgot your camera at home? You can also take high-quality 9MP digital still photos and then flip through them on your HDTV with family and friends.', 1, 'Samsung__HMX-R10', 'Samsung  HMX-R10', 'This ultra-compact camcorder adds an extra level of comfort to every shot you take. Its ergonomic de', 'Samsung  HMX-R10 undefined', 'An ultra-compact, ergonomic design with a smooth, curvy shape lets you hold the camcorder in total comfort. That means you''re always ready to get the best shot and capture more memories. The lens is also angled at 25 degrees, which reduces the strain on your wrist and helps you to relax, record, smile.'),
(38, 3, 'Samsung HMX-H106', 'The best way to relive special moments is by watching them in amazing high definition on your HDTV. The best way to do this is with the Samsung HMX-H106 camcorder. Record up to 12 hours of full HD (1920x1080 resolution) content with the included battery for breathtaking images in brilliant color. It also includes 10x optical zoom so you can get close to the action and optical image stabilizer for blur-free video.\n\n64GB SSD\nThe SC-HMX-H106 has 64 GB of built-in flash memory so you never miss anything. Samsung''s SSD technology is faster than HDD, including quicker boot-up and read/write speeds which is required for the amount of data recorded in full-HD resolution. Samsung''s SSD technology consumes approximately 1/8th of the power of a comparable HDD.\n\nFull HD (1920 x 1080/60i or 30p)\nNow you can watch your videos in full high definition. That means crystal-clear details, the sharpest picture quality available and brilliant color. The 1/4.5" CMOS imaging sensor boasts 2.2 mega-pixels and yields impressive light sensitivity to capture full HD video at 1920 x 1080 lines of resolution.\n10x Optical Zoom\nWith its high quality 10x optical zoom lens you can get close to the action from a safe distance. Now you can see it all in perfect detail.\n', 0, 'Samsung_HMX-H106', 'Samsung HMX-H106', 'The best way to relive special moments is by watching them in amazing high definition on your HDTV. ', 'Samsung HMX-H106 undefined', 'The best way to relive special moments is by watching them in amazing high definition on your HDTV. The best way to do this is with the Samsung HMX-H106 camcorder. Record up to 12 hours of full HD (1920x1080 resolution) content with the included battery for breathtaking images in brilliant color. It also includes 10x optical zoom so you can get close to the action and optical image stabilizer for blur-free video.');
