(62, 1, 'Ducati Grand Prix ', 'The Ducati Race Track features two mini remote-controlled bikes modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes. By grasping the infrared handle bar, your child can drive the mini Ducati bikes around the curves and over the bumps of the Grand Prix racetrack. The Ducati Race Track includes accessories like a start line, pit stop, crash barriers, and advertising boards and even features real Grand Prix Race Track sounds effects. Donâ€™t forget to check out Chiccoâ€™s Remote Control Ducati Motorcycles. ', 1, 'Ducati_Grand_Prix_', 'Ducati Grand Prix ', 'The Ducati Race Track features two mini remote-controlled bikes modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance', 'Ducati Grand Prix  undefined', '    * Features two mini remote-controlled Ducati motorcycles and a Grand Prix Race Track\n    * Motorcycles designed after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes\n    * Drive the bikes on or off the Grand Prix Racetrack\n    * Includes accessories like a start line, pit stop, crash barriers, and advertising boards\n    * For children ages 2 years and up\n    * Requires: 8 x AA batteries (not included)'),
