(39, 2, 'Samsung HMX-20C', 'You wonâ€™t miss any of lifeâ€™s special moments with this compact, lightweight camcorder. The SAMSUNG SC-HMX20C has an amazing built-in 8 GB of flash memory for 90 minutes of recording time. Plus, with the 2.7-inch touch screen LCD and a convenient swivel handgrip, youâ€™ll easily capture odd-angle shots like babyâ€™s first steps. Full HD recording with 1080p delivers breathtaking images and brilliant resolution.', 2, 'Samsung_HMX-20C', 'Samsung HMX-20C', 'You wonâ€™t miss any of lifeâ€™s special moments with this compact, lightweight camcorder. The SAMSUNG S', 'Samsung HMX-20C undefined', 'With its high quality 10x optical zoom and 100x digital zoom lens you can get close to the action from a safe distance. And for those ultra long distance shots, the 100x digital zoom will let you see it all in perfect detail.'),
(40, 2, 'Panasonic HDC-TM300', 'HD images contain 6 times as much information as standard images. HDTV has 1,080 horizontal scan lines, SDTV has 480. That translates into much higher resolution and much finer detail. With HD images on an HDTV, pictures are so clear and sharp that you can see textures. The shift in the industry from SDTV to HDTV is well underway. For shooting once-in-a-lifetime scenes that you want to capture in full beauty, an HD camcorder is the best choice.\n\n3MOS System for Beautiful Images\nFor videos of important moments you want to preserve, you want high image quality. That''s what Panasonic''s 3MOS System delivers, with a combination of optical technologies that further enhance the quality of full-HD images. The 3MOS System produces extremely accurate images with superb rendition of differences in darkness and light, rich color expression, and a full 1,080 lines of horizontal resolution. This advanced technology helps turn once-in-a-lifetime moments into vivid, beautiful images.\n\niA (Intelligent Auto) for Smart Control\nThere''s nothing more disappointing than shooting a once-in-a-lifetime event on video, only to discover that the images are blurry or poorly exposed because of backlighting. Panasonic''s iA helps avoid problems in difficult shooting situations by automatically making the optimal camera settings and activating certain functions. For example, iA now includes AF Tracking, a new function that "locks" on and follows a subject as it moves, so images are sharply focused and properly exposed. This technology is a huge help for everyone.\n\nAdvanced O.I.S. (Optical Image Stabilization)\nPanasonic''s advanced O.I.S. helps suppress the effects of hand-shake as you shoot, for both motion and still images. This system uses gyrosensors to detect even tiny amounts of hand-shake, then shifts a lens and adjusts the optical axis to compensate - all at an astounding 4,000 times per second. It also covers approximately 3 times the stabilization area of our previous SD9 model. Because the system is optical, there''s only minimal loss of image quality even when viewed on a large-screen TV. In addition, to shoot high-resolution still images, the normal O.I.S. Mode 1 is joined by an O.I.S. Mode 2, which has a higher stabilization capability. The O.I.S. corrective lens shifts and stabilizes the image the instant that the shutter button is pressed, to enable greater precision in stabilization. You get all the beauty and minimal blurring.\n\nGet Creative - Advanced Functions for Serious Video Shooting\n\nCraft images with intuitive ease: Manual Ring\nThe manual ring gives you easy, fingertip control over the focus, zoom and exposure settings. You''ll find using the ring a much more intuitive, comfortable, user-friendly process than accessing a menu screen. With the manual ring and manual operation, the TM300 is a pleasure to use and gives you the freedom to craft unusually expressive images.\nZoom\nJust rotate the ring to zoom in and out. You have full control of the zooming speed and can zoom in or out to the precise degree you want.\nFocus\nJust rotate the ring to focus. You can focus on the exact point you want, even if it''s not in the center of the frame. You can also change the focus as you shoot, to get the kind of creative shots you sometimes see in movies.\nWhite Balance\nSelect from Auto, Indoor, Outdoor, and White Set according to the location, weather, or type of lighting. You''ll always get the best possible coloring even if the light source changes. *Only when using the EVF.\nShutter Speed\nThe shutter speed can be adjusted from 1/24 to 1/8,000 of a second. Use a high shutter speed when shooting sports events or fast-moving subjects, and you can get clear, sharp, incredible action shots. *Only when using the EVF.\nIris\nUse the ring to adjust the aperture to regulate the amount of light let in. In dim lighting use a lower aperture setting (which corresponds to a larger aperture opening), and in bright lighting use a higher setting. *Only when using the EVF.\n\nA precise way to check the lighting: On-Screen Assist\nZebra Pattern\nA "zebra pattern" is displayed in areas of the frame where the lighting is excessive and the image is over-exposed.\nBrightness Level\nThe light level is metered at the center of the frame and displayed as a percentage (%). This serves as a guide when you''re shooting a subject that''s backlit, or when you want to keep the light level the same even though the lighting conditions change.\nHistogram\nThe histogram displays in graph form the exposure and contrast conditions over the entire frame. This lets you determine fine gradation details that are difficult to tell by just looking at the screen.\n\nTime Lapse Recording\nThe time lapse function uses longer frame intervals than standard shooting. You can use this function to capture shortened or condensed footage of events that actually take place over a much longer time period. For example, time lapse recording is ideal for shooting a flower in the process of blooming, or a long, slow sunset. With time lapse recording, you have an interesting new video technique to explore. *The maximum continuous recording time is 12 hours.', 11, 'Panasonic_HDC-TM300', 'Panasonic HDC-TM300', 'HD images contain 6 times as much information as standard images. HDTV has 1,080 horizontal scan lin', 'Panasonic HDC-TM300 undefined', 'HD images contain 6 times as much information as standard images. HDTV has 1,080 horizontal scan lines, SDTV has 480. That translates into much higher resolution and much finer detail. With HD images on an HDTV, pictures are so clear and sharp that you can see textures. The shift in the industry from SDTV to HDTV is well underway. For shooting once-in-a-lifetime scenes that you want to capture in full beauty, an HD camcorder is the best choice.'),
(41, 2, 'Panasonic HDC-HS9', 'HDD + SD = Up to 29 Hours of Recording Time\nThe HDC-HS9 hi-def hybrid camcorder boasts an extra-large 60GB* internal hard disk drive, which can hold up to 23 hours of your precious memories (in HE mode). And since this camcorder records to both the internal hard drive and SD card, you can add up to an additional six hours of recording (also in HE mode) onto a 16GB* SDHC memory card (sold seperately).\n\n*1 GB = one billion bytes. Usable capacity will be less.\n\nNever Miss a Detail with 1920x1080 Full-HD Recording\nPanasonic full-HD camcorders record horizontal pixels at an HD resolution of up to 1920 pixels, which results in a total of around 2,070,000 pixels. And with progressive scanning, our hi-def camcorders provide twice as much data per picture as conventional interlace scanning. This means you get breathtaking images with exceptional resolution and detail. Combine that with a 1080/24p format, which lets you capture scenes with a rich, film-like quality, and you can see why Panasonic full-HD camcorders take visual expression to the next level. ', 1, 'Panasonic_HDC-HS9', 'Panasonic HDC-HS9', 'HDD + SD = Up to 29 Hours of Recording Time\nThe HDC-HS9 hi-def hybrid camcorder boasts an extra-larg', 'Panasonic HDC-HS9 undefined', '60GB 3CCD Hard Disk Drive/SD Hybrid Full-High Definition Camcorder with 1920x1080-Pixel Recording, Advanced Optical Image Stabilizer, Leica Lens, 10x Optical Zoom, Face Detection and 5.1 Surround Sound, Records to Internal Hard Drive and SD Memory Card'),
(42, 2, 'HTC Hero', 'With HTC Hero, personalization reaches a level never before possible. Rather than burying important content under layers of menus, the HTC Hero lets you put it at glance view, with a selection of widgets that can be placed right on the home screen. The widgets themselves can be personalized with a variety of designs and sizes that best match your personality.\n\nWith Scenes, a new profile feature, HTC Hero becomes multiple phones in one. Create and switch between Scenes that reflect different moments in your life. Your Hero becomes a weekend phone that helps you relax with your choice of tunes, catch up with your favorite friends and capture some memories with HTC Footprintsâ„¢. And when you go on a trip, your phone becomes your personal guide and gives you instant access to local time, weather and maps.\n \nStay Close\nToday, staying in touch with the people in your life means managing a variety of communication channels and applications ranging from phone calls and emails to Facebook updates. HTC Hero makes staying close as simple as turning to your friend and saying hello. When you view people, you see the different ways to get in touch, you also see all your interactions like emails sent to your personal and work accounts. You can even check for social network updates and event notices as well as see the latest pictures your friends uploaded to popular photo sharing sites.\n \nDiscover the Unexpected\nMany of the most memorable moments in your life are experienced, not explained. Even basic functions like the dialer will pleasantly surprise you on the HTC Hero. You can find a person by dialing their phone number or simply by dialing the first few letters of their name.\n\nWith HTC Hero, you can look at things through different perspectives. Your inbox is not just a list of emails, but a catalog of conversations, a collection of notes flagged as important, and a document library of all your emails with attachments. Your Album is not just the photos saved on your phone. It is also a gateway to online collections of you and your friends on Facebook or Flickr.\n\nSearch just about anything, anywhere on your HTC Hero. The dedicated Search button combs through tweets in Twitterâ„¢, locates people in your contact list, finds emails in your inbox, searches through appointments in the calendar and very nearly finds needles in haystacks.', 45, 'HTC_Hero', 'HTC Hero', 'With HTC Hero, personalization reaches a level never before possible. Rather than burying important ', 'HTC Hero undefined', 'HTC Hero is our first phone to embody HTC Senseâ„¢ - an intuitive, seamless experience built upon three fundamental principles - make it mine, stay close, and discover the unexpected.'),
(43, 2, 'HTC HD2', 'HTC HD2 delivers an experience your senses have been waiting for. The unprecedented 4.3-inch pixel-packed display is stunning. The worldâ€™s first capacitive touch technology on a WindowsÂ® phone along with 1 GHz processing power ensure a smooth and lightning-fast response to the lightest touch of your finger.\n\nMost importantly, it is our first Windows phone to embody HTC Senseâ„¢ - a holistic experience that focuses on making phones work in the most intuitive way. HTC Sense is based on three core principles â€“ make it mine, stay close, and discover the unexpected.\n \nMake It Mine 	Make It Mine\nHTC HD2â€™s expansive display is like a canvas on which you create a phone that is just right for you. Customize the phone by prioritizing essential features like mail, calendar, messaging, browser and more. Next, with just a tap, put shortcuts to the most important people, favorite websites, or most used application right on the home screen. And if you feel like something is still missing, visit WindowsÂ® Marketplace for Mobile, and install fun and useful applications.\n\nYour phone doesn''t only reflect your personality; it also tunes into your location. The clock automatically updates to the local time wherever you are. You can see the outside temperature and weather at a glance. And, if you choose the weather wallpaper, you''ll get a brilliantly lifelike animation that lets you virtually feel the sunâ€™s rays or the chill of the breeze without setting a foot outside.\n \nStay Close\nWith HTC HD2, communication is focused around people rather than applications, so all of your interactions like email, SMS, phone logs, and even updates from Facebook are all in one place. Right where your instinct tells you to look â€“ next to the photo of the person with whom you want to stay in touch with.\n\nIn business, a phone call often has the power to prevent a mile-long pile up of inconclusive emails. HTC HD2 makes it simple to go from reading an email to calling the sender. All it takes is a single tap on the large phone icon right from the email. And if you need to get everyone involved in the discussion â€“ just tap next to the images of everyone to create an instant conference call.\n\nForget the challenge of jumping from your calendar to your phone application while trying to find and memorize the number for your next conference call. On HTC HD2, conference call reminders conveniently appear with a big dial button ready for you to press, even the PIN is displayed, so youâ€™ll never miss out on the latest strategy session.', 8, 'HTC_HD2', 'HTC HD2', 'HTC HD2 delivers an experience your senses have been waiting for. The unprecedented 4.3-inch pixel-p', 'HTC HD2 undefined', 'HTC HD2 delivers an experience your senses have been waiting for. The unprecedented 4.3-inch pixel-packed display is stunning. The worldâ€™s first capacitive touch technology on a WindowsÂ® phone along with 1 GHz processing power ensure a smooth and lightning-fast response to the lightest touch of your finger.'),
(44, 2, 'HTC Tatoo', 'HTC Tattoo is all about you. Itâ€™s the first phone that can be customized inside and out. Decide how your phone looks, then decide what you want to look at. Texts? Twitter? Your photos? When youâ€™re done customizing HTC Tattoo, youâ€™ll have a phone that speaks loudly about who you are and what youâ€™re into.\n\nMake it Mine\nYour phone is by your side 24/7 and looks do matter. With HTC Tattoo, you donâ€™t just pick the look, you make the look, by designing your own personal skin for the phone. Next, you decide what really matters to you on your phone. So if youâ€™re into chatting, texting, and tweeting, youâ€™ll put all your communication widgets and apps right on your front screen. If youâ€™re into games, youâ€™ll visit Android Market and download all the games you want. Put them right on the surface - ready to kill boredom whenever it tries to come out.\n\nStay Close\nDo you have a friend like Jack? Jack â€“ sends you 4 SMS/hour, 3 emails/day, updates his facebook status constantly and uploads pictures on Flickr that you just canâ€™t miss. With HTC Tattoo staying on top of Jackâ€™s and your other friendsâ€™ lives is dead easy. All you have to do is find a friendly face and your interactions are there, all in one place. So there is no more jumping from one app to another.\n\nDiscover the Unexpected\nSometimes there are no words to describe the cool surprises that happen in your life. Even basic functions like the dialer will make you smile on the HTC Tattoo. You can find a friend by dialing their phone number or simply by dialing their name.\n\nIf youâ€™re into music, youâ€™ll love the way you can organize all your tunes by album, artist or by playlists you create. And if youâ€™re a photo fan, youâ€™ll rave about the fact that your Album is not just the photos saved on your phone. It is also a gateway to online collections of you and your friends on Facebook or Flickr.\n\nFinding needles in a haystack is no longer a problem with HTC Tattoo. The dedicated Search button sifts through tweets in Twitter?, locates friends in your contact list, finds emails in your inbox, searches through events in the calendar, and scours the web for info.', 9, 'HTC_Tatoo', 'HTC Tatoo', 'HTC Tattoo is all about you. Itâ€™s the first phone that can be customized inside and out. Decide how ', 'HTC Tatoo undefined', 'HTC Tattoo is all about you. Itâ€™s the first phone that can be customized inside and out. Decide how your phone looks, then decide what you want to look at. Texts? Twitter? Your photos? When youâ€™re done customizing HTC Tattoo, youâ€™ll have a phone that speaks loudly about who you are and what youâ€™re into.'),
(46, 2, 'Samsung Omnia i-910', 'With the SAMSUNG Omniaâ„¢, SAMSUNG has created a phone that truly gives you everything you want â€“ just a touch away. You get a customizable touchscreen with drag-and-drop widgets, the convenience of Windows MobileÂ® 6.1 Professional, a full HTML Web browser, music player, video player, Wi-Fi network connectability and an incredible 5.0 megapixel camera that just might make your regular digital camera obsolete. As we said, Omniaâ„¢ gives you everything. All you have to do is enjoy it.', 1, 'Samsung_Omnia_i-910', 'Samsung Omnia i-910', 'With the SAMSUNG Omniaâ„¢, SAMSUNG has created a phone that truly gives you everything you want â€“ just', 'Samsung Omnia i-910 undefined', 'With the SAMSUNG Omniaâ„¢, SAMSUNG has created a phone that truly gives you everything you want â€“ just a touch away. You get a customizable touchscreen with drag-and-drop widgets, the convenience of Windows MobileÂ® 6.1 Professional, a full HTML Web browser, music player, video player, Wi-Fi network connectability and an incredible 5.0 megapixel camera that just might make your regular digital camera obsolete. As we said, Omniaâ„¢ gives you everything. All you have to do is enjoy it.'),
(47, 2, 'SonyEricsson X1', 'XPERIAâ„¢ panel interface\n\nEnjoy access to different experiences - Web, multimedia, applications - from your desktop. Navigate with the tip of your finger. Configure and have your XPERIAâ„¢ panels just the way you want them.\nXPERIAâ„¢ X1a lets you interact via numerous intuitive ways. Touch, full QWERTY, 4-way key and optical joystick - you switch seamlessly between operation modes.The arc design gives XPERIAâ„¢ X1a a distinctive and unique look. Slide the screen upwards to reveal the wide-pitch QWERTY keyboard.Quick and easy access to broadband Internet. Say hello to video calls, audio and video streaming, internet surfing, multimedia messaging and email on the go.Text input using stylus on touchscreen: write a character as you would with a pen, and it transforms it into the corresponding letter on a keyboard.', 6, 'SonyEricsson_X1', 'SonyEricsson X1', 'XPERIAâ„¢ panel interface\n\nEnjoy access to different experiences - Web, multimedia, applications - fro', 'SonyEricsson X1 undefined', 'Life is mobile. Let everything that is important to you be with you all the time. The people in your life, the Internet, your music, pictures and video.'),
(48, 2, 'SonyEricsson TM506', 'TM506 Features\nIntegrated camera\nIntegrated camera\n\nBuilt-in digital camera with screen viewfinder, dedicated menus and direct interaction with in-phone imaging and messaging features.\nVideo blog\nVideo blog\n\nYou get your own personal blog site with your phone. So why not add some moving pictures to it? Shoot a video clip, and all it takes to upload it is a few clicks.\nBlog your life\nBlog your life\n\nThe easy way to share your life in pictures. Take or choose a photo, add a little text and publish it for friends and family to enjoy. Learn more about picture blogging\nMMS\nMMS\n\nTake a picture of where you are, record or write a greeting and send to any MMS-capable phone or email address. Send pictures, text, sound and video.\nPush email\nPush email\n\nInstant email on your mobile phone, just like on your home computer. Messages are sent directly to your phone as soon as they arrive.\n', 1, 'SonyEricsson_TM506', 'SonyEricsson TM506', 'TM506 Features\nIntegrated camera\nIntegrated camera\n\nBuilt-in digital camera with screen viewfinder, ', 'SonyEricsson TM506 undefined', 'The stylish Sony Ericsson TM506 keeps you in-the-know and on-the-go. Share your tunes, pick a flick, call the crew, find a lunch spot or capture the moment. Exclusively available at T-Mobile.'),
(49, 2, 'LG Chocolate BL40', 'Mobile Phone with 4.0â€ WVGA TFT touchscreen, Dual Screen UI, 5 MP Camera\n\nThe new LG Chocolate BL40 phone has a 4.0-inch wide HD LCD screen with 800x345 pixel resolution to maximize visual experience. The wide HD LCD â€œReal VGAâ€ screen presents a vibrant range of natural colours, allowing photos to appear sharper, videos more true-to-life, games naturally vivid and documents more readable.', 29, 'LG_Chocolate_BL40', 'LG Chocolate BL40', 'Mobile Phone with 4.0â€ WVGA TFT touchscreen, Dual Screen UI, 5 MP Camera\n\nThe new LG Chocolate BL40 ', 'LG Chocolate BL40 undefined', 'Mobile Phone with 4.0â€ WVGA TFT touchscreen, Dual Screen UI, 5 MP Camera\n\nThe new LG Chocolate BL40 phone has a 4.0-inch wide HD LCD screen with 800x345 pixel resolution to maximize visual experience. The wide HD LCD â€œReal VGAâ€ screen presents a vibrant range of natural colours, allowing photos to appear sharper, videos more true-to-life, games naturally vivid and documents more readable.'),
(50, 2, 'Nokia n97 mini', '    *  Personalise your home screen with widgets that bring live feeds from social networks, news agencies, and weather services.\n    * Add bookmarks and contact shortcuts to your home screen so that your favourite webpages and friends are just a tap away.\n    * Stay in control of your email, calendar, and music with dedicated widgets for your home screen.\n    * Move content around your home screen and place it anywhere you like by dragging your finger across the multi-sensory display.\n', 2, 'Nokia_n97_mini', 'Nokia n97 mini', '    *  Personalise your home screen with widgets that bring live feeds from social networks, news ag', 'Nokia n97 mini undefined', '    *  Personalise your home screen with widgets that bring live feeds from social networks, news agencies, and weather services.\n'),
(51, 2, 'Nokia N900', '    *  No need to carry a netbook. Have a compact device the size of a handset with a large, high-resolution screen.\n    * Keep multiple web windows open. The Maemo browser is powered by Mozilla technology.\n    * Use the full web faster over high speed HSPA and WLAN connections.\n    * Watch videos, use internet applications and play games with full Adobe Flash 9.4TM and AJAX support.\n    * Enjoy fast and easy browsing with gestures and full QWERTY keyboard.\n\nNokia N900\nPhone & Contacts\n\n    * Merge your phone book, Skype contacts and other contacts into an all-in-one address book.\n    * Always stay online - see your friendsâ€™ availability, avatars, location and mood.\n    * Tap your friends and select the best way to contact them: via a regular phone call, Instant Messaging, SMS, email or an Internet call.\n    * Synchronise your contacts to Outlook.\n    * Keep multiple SMS & IM conversations going and move easily between them.\n\nNokia N900\nEmail & Calendar\n\n    * Easily set up multiple email accounts with support for popular email providers.\n    * Push Email, calendar and contacts with Mail for Exchange.\n    * Slide out the full keyboard designed for fast typing. Speed your typing up further with smart on-screen features and word completion.\n    * See images, web links and open attachments in your email with rich HTML support, like on a PC.\n\n', 7, 'Nokia_N900', 'Nokia N900', '    *  No need to carry a netbook. Have a compact device the size of a handset with a large, high-re', 'Nokia N900 undefined', '# No need to carry a netbook. Have a compact device the size of a handset with a large, high-resolution screen.\n# Keep multiple web windows open. The Maemo browser is powered by Mozilla technology.'),
(52, 2, 'HTC BH M300 Bluetooth Mono Headset', 'The HTC BH M300 is a wireless mono headset, which utilizes Bluetooth technology and is designed to be used when talking handsfree or whilst driving.\n\nThe small, lightweight bluetooth streaming music headset is comfortable to wear and easy to pair.\n\nBH M300 is easy to pair with every bluetooth enabled mobile. The DSP (Digital Signal Processing) inside the BH M200 provides sophisticated duplex, echo cancellation and noise reduction technology, which ensures high audio sound quality for the end user.\n\nIt is designed for you to wear without the earhook, this headset is secured by an ear-gel piece. It features simple controls through three buttons on the top and one side. ', 1, 'HTC_BH_M300_Bluetooth_Mono_Headset', 'HTC BH M300 Bluetooth Mono Headset', 'The HTC BH M300 is a wireless mono headset, which utilizes Bluetooth technology and is designed to b', 'HTC BH M300 Bluetooth Mono Headset undefined', 'The HTC BH M300 is a wireless mono headset, which utilizes Bluetooth technology and is designed to be used when talking handsfree or whilst driving.\n'),
(53, 2, 'HTC Multifunction Audio Cable YC A300', 'This fantastic multifunctional cable ExtUSB (6 pin) connector allows users to connect a range of audio cables to their device. You only need to carry one adaptor.\n\nN.B. This new product replaces the existing YC A100 Y-cable and YC A200 Multifunctional cable. The cable allows for simultaneous charging and talking via a wired headset. ', 0, 'HTC_Multifunction_Audio_Cable_YC_A300', 'HTC Multifunction Audio Cable YC A300', 'This fantastic multifunctional cable ExtUSB (6 pin) connector allows users to connect a range of aud', 'HTC Multifunction Audio Cable YC A300 undefined', '    * HTC ExtUSB standard headset connector\n    * Mini USB power connector\n    * 3.5mm audio connector (with in-line mic support)\n    * 2.5mm audio connector (with in-line mic support)\n    * Power status light'),
(54, 2, 'HTC Battery Bank BB G300', 'With the high capacity of 2680 mAh, the BB G300 Battery bank provides the ability to charge your device up to three times when mains power is not available (depending on usage and battery capacity). The HTC BB G300 is fitted with both USB and mini USB ports for your convenience and a multi-level charge indicator, the HTC BB G300 is the perfect solution to charging when you are on the move.\n\nN.B. The BB G300 is an alternative solution to older HTC and Qtek models where spare batteries are no longer available. ', 0, 'HTC_Battery_Bank_BB_G300', 'HTC Battery Bank BB G300', 'With the high capacity of 2680 mAh, the BB G300 Battery bank provides the ability to charge your dev', 'HTC Battery Bank BB G300 undefined', '    * Cell capacity: 2680mAh\n    * Input: 5VDC, 1000 mA (for AC adapter) & 500 mA (miniUSB)\n    * Output: 5VDC, 1000 mA (USB-A)\n    * Connectors:\n      - Female standard USB connector(for charging the device from battery bank via the USB cable)\n      - Female mini USB connector(for charging battery bank from USB cable or AC adapter)'),
(55, 2, 'HTC Desktop Cradle CR G300 for Variant Models', 'Charge or synchronise your HTC Touch Diamond//Touch Pro/Touch 3G/Touch Viva/S740/P3470/Touch Diamond2/Touch Pro2, simply by placing the device in the cradle connector. You can plug the desktop cradle into a home stereo system with a line in or AUX connector via the cradleâ€™s 3.5mm line out connection to enjoy high quality music playback.\n\nIt can be charged and synchronised with HTC Touch Diamond AC Adaptor UK TC B100 (not included) or HTC Touch Diamond Data Cable DC U300 (USB/ExtUSB)(not included) or HTC Touch Diamond mini USB Data Cable DC U100 (not included).\n\nThis cradle comes with seven inserts (the plastic holders): one insert for Touch Diamond and T-Mobile MDA Compact IV; one insert for Touch Diamond and T-Mobile MDA Compact IV extended batteries; one insert for Touch Pro and T-Mobile MDA Vario IV; one insert for P3470; one insert for S740; one insert for Touch 3G and one insert for Touch Viva. These inserts can be bought separately HTC Touch Diamond Desktop Cradle Insert, HTC Touch Diamond Desktop Cradle Insert (for Extended Battery),HTC Touch Pro Desktop Cradle Insert; HTC P3470 Desktop Cradle CR G300 Insert if you need the spare ones.\n\nThe CR G300 cradle also supports the inline connection of the following optional accessories:\n- HTC Touch Diamond Multifunction Audio Cable YC A300', 0, 'HTC_Desktop_Cradle_CR_G300_for_Variant_Models', 'HTC Desktop Cradle CR G300 for Variant Models', 'Charge or synchronise your HTC Touch Diamond//Touch Pro/Touch 3G/Touch Viva/S740/P3470/Touch Diamond', 'HTC Desktop Cradle CR G300 for Variant Models undefined', 'Charge or synchronise your HTC Touch Diamond//Touch Pro/Touch 3G/Touch Viva/S740/P3470/Touch Diamond2/Touch Pro2, simply by placing the device in the cradle connector. You can plug the desktop cradle into a home stereo system with a line in or AUX connector via the cradleâ€™s 3.5mm line out connection to enjoy high quality music playback. '),
(56, 2, 'MicroUSB Bluetooth Headse  WEP850', 'The SAMSUNG WEP850 Bluetooth Headset is highly fashionable & highly functional. Unique in design, the WEP850 has a high-gloss, lacquer finish with diamond-cut accents. Carry on amazingly crystal clear communications anytime with its dual-microphone noise/echo-cancelation technology that eliminates unwanted background noise. The Digital Signal Processing (DSP) technology digitally compares the signals from the two microphones & subtracts the common background noise resulting in clearer communications. The Multipoint Technology allows direct connectivity between the headset & two mobile phones. Talk on and on with the WEP850 with up to 8 hours talk time & up to 250 hours standby time. Package includes WEP850 Headset, MicroUSB Travel Adapter, Detachable Ear Hook, & User Manual. Universally compatible with SAMSUNG & non-SAMSUNG Bluetooth enabled phones. Charge on the go with SAMSUNG''s optional MicroUSB Car Charger available for purchase separately, part # CAD300UBEB/STD.', 0, 'MicroUSB_Bluetooth_Headse__WEP850', 'MicroUSB Bluetooth Headse  WEP850', 'The SAMSUNG WEP850 Bluetooth Headset is highly fashionable & highly functional. Unique in design, th', 'MicroUSB Bluetooth Headse  WEP850 undefined', 'The SAMSUNG WEP850 Bluetooth Headset is highly fashionable & highly functional.'),
(57, 2, 'Clear Screen Protector', '\nClear Screen Protector\n\nThis screen protector''s unique material protects your SAMSUNG a877 Impression against scratching and abrasion. The surface is not textured like other screen protectors, but the smooth feeling of your wireless device''s display is left unchanged. The screen protector is very easy to apply and remove, and can give your SAMSUNG Impression handset the special look & added protection it deserves. Package includes 2 Clear Screen Protectors & a soft cloth.\n', 1, 'Clear_Screen_Protector', 'Clear Screen Protector', '\nClear Screen Protector\n\nThis screen protector''s unique material protects your SAMSUNG a877 Impressi', 'Clear Screen Protector undefined', '\nClear Screen Protector\n\nThis screen protector''s unique material protects your SAMSUNG a877 Impression against scratching and abrasion. The surface is not textured like other screen protectors, but the smooth feeling of your wireless device''s display is left unchanged. The screen protector is very easy to apply and remove, and can give your SAMSUNG Impression handset the special look & added protection it deserves. Package includes 2 Clear Screen Protectors & a soft cloth.\n'),
(58, 2, 'Samsung WEP870 Convertible Mono and Stereo Bluetooth Headset ', 'Take the latest technology in Bluetooth audio and entertainment with you in one convenient package with the WEP870 convertible mono and stereo music streaming headset. This brilliant device not only provides advanced, dual microphone noise cancellation for crystal clear conversations, it easily converts to a stereo, music streaming wonder with the included adjustable stereo ear bud lanyard. Plus, the WEP870 allows you to take calls in mono and stereo mode, gently fading your music when a call comes in then returning to your music when your call ends. Talk Time/Play Time: Up to 6 hours Standby time: Up to 150 hours Dedicated on/off switch Detachable Crystal Clear Earhook', 1, 'Samsung_WEP870_Convertible_Mono_and_Stereo_Bluetooth_Headset_', 'Samsung WEP870 Convertible Mono and Stereo Bluetooth Headset ', 'Take the latest technology in Bluetooth audio and entertainment with you in one convenient package w', 'Samsung WEP870 Convertible Mono and Stereo Bluetooth Headset  undefined', 'Take the latest technology in Bluetooth audio and entertainment with you in one convenient package with the WEP870 convertible mono and stereo music streaming headset.'),
(59, 2, 'Horizontal Black Pouch', 'This sleekly designed Horizontal Black Pouch was crafted to ensure protection of your SAMSUNG wireless phone as well as withstand wear and tear. This pouch is ideal if you want to carry your wireless phone at your waist side. Features a non-removable swivel clip.', 2, '_Horizontal_Black_Pouch', ' Horizontal Black Pouch', 'This sleekly designed Horizontal Black Pouch was crafted to ensure protection of your SAMSUNG wirele', ' Horizontal Black Pouch undefined', 'This sleekly designed Horizontal Black Pouch was crafted to ensure protection of your SAMSUNG wireless phone as well as withstand wear and tear. This pouch is ideal if you want to carry your wireless phone at your waist side. Features a non-removable swivel clip.'),
(60, 2, 'Universal Stylus with Strap', 'The SAMSUNG retractable Universal Black Stylus is practical, fashionable and allows you to easily navigate and use your SAMSUNG touchscreen wireless phone with ease. Includes a removable strap. This stylus is also compatible with non-SAMSUNG touchscreen devices.\n', 1, '_Universal_Stylus_with_Strap', ' Universal Stylus with Strap', 'The SAMSUNG retractable Universal Black Stylus is practical, fashionable and allows you to easily na', ' Universal Stylus with Strap undefined', 'The SAMSUNG retractable Universal Black Stylus is practical, fashionable and allows you to easily navigate and use your SAMSUNG touchscreen wireless phone with ease. Includes a removable strap. '),
(61, 2, 'Chiccolini Flower Chic', 'Flower Chic is the new collection of Chiccolini dolls inspired by the very latest trends in fashion. The dolls come in three unique bags, made from a new â€œshinyâ€ material, and decorated with three â€œjeweledâ€ flowers. A trendy fashion accessory for the child.', 3, 'Chiccolini_Flower_Chic', 'Chiccolini Flower Chic', 'Flower Chic is the new collection of Chiccolini dolls inspired by the very latest trends in fashion.', 'Chiccolini Flower Chic undefined', '    * Shiny carry bag\n    * Embellished with jeweled flowers\n    * Bright colors make a trendy accessory\n    * Great for children ages 3 years and up'),
(62, 2, 'Ducati Grand Prix ', 'The Ducati Race Track features two mini remote-controlled bikes modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes. By grasping the infrared handle bar, your child can drive the mini Ducati bikes around the curves and over the bumps of the Grand Prix racetrack. The Ducati Race Track includes accessories like a start line, pit stop, crash barriers, and advertising boards and even features real Grand Prix Race Track sounds effects. Donâ€™t forget to check out Chiccoâ€™s Remote Control Ducati Motorcycles. ', 1, 'Ducati_Grand_Prix_', 'Ducati Grand Prix ', 'The Ducati Race Track features two mini remote-controlled bikes modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance', 'Ducati Grand Prix  undefined', '    * Features two mini remote-controlled Ducati motorcycles and a Grand Prix Race Track\n    * Motorcycles designed after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes\n    * Drive the bikes on or off the Grand Prix Racetrack\n    * Includes accessories like a start line, pit stop, crash barriers, and advertising boards\n    * For children ages 2 years and up\n    * Requires: 8 x AA batteries (not included)'),
(63, 2, 'Ct 0.5 Doll Stroller', 'Chiccoâ€™s Ct.5 Doll Stroller is a great accessory for your daughterâ€™s dolls. Designed just like Chiccoâ€™s Ct0.5 Stroller, this mini stroller is fully accessorized. It is easy to fold and has front swivel wheels, a reclining backrest, a storage basket, and a sun canopy. Check out more Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, and the Mini Chicco Pram. The Mini Chicco accessories are designed for children ages 3 and older.', 0, 'Ct_0.5_Doll_Stroller', 'Ct 0.5 Doll Stroller', 'Chiccoâ€™s Ct.5 Doll Stroller is a great accessory for your daughterâ€™s dolls. Designed just like Chicc', 'Ct 0.5 Doll Stroller undefined', '    *  Designed after the Chicco Ct0.5 Stroller\n    * Holds up to a 22" doll\n    * Fully accessorized: front swivel wheels, a reclining backrest, a storage basket, and a sun canopy\n    * Matches all the Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, and the Mini Chicco Pram\n    * For children ages 3 years and up\n'),
(64, 2, 'Radio Control ATV', 'The Radio Control ATV is a great introduction to the big kids world of remote control cars for your child as young as 2 years old. This brightly colored, smiling car comes with a remote control that attaches to the car and becomes the spare tire. The remote control comes with large buttons for little hands and controls the car in four directions. The Radio Control ATV will also improve your child''s coordination skills and will encourage creativity.', 4, 'Radio_Control_ATV', 'Radio Control ATV', 'The Radio Control ATV is a great introduction to the big kids world of remote control cars for your ', 'Radio Control ATV undefined', '    *  Remote Control Car for children as young as 2 years old\n    * Attachable remote control that becomes a spare tire\n    * Four large direction buttons for little hands\n    * Promotes creativity and improves coordination skills\n    * Requires: 4 x AA & 3 x AAA batteries (not included)'),
(65, 2, 'Billy Fun Wheels ', 'Make way for Billy Fun Wheels, the first motion-sensing remote control monster truck for children 2 years and up! The intuitive remote control is shaped just like a steering wheel, and rotating it makes the truck turn left or right. Arrows on the steering remote light up to help the child understand which way the truck will head. Engine sounds and working headlights add to the realism of  "driving" the truck, and a fun honk warns everybody that Billy is here! ', 2, 'Billy_Fun_Wheels_', 'Billy Fun Wheels ', 'Make way for Billy Fun Wheels, the first motion-sensing remote control monster truck for children 2 ', 'Billy Fun Wheels  undefined', '    *  The first motion-controlled monster truck for preschoolers!\n    * Intuitive steering wheel can be rotated left or right to steer the truck\n    * Realistic engine, reverse capability, and honking sounds add to the fun\n    * Headlights light up - all the better for those nighttime races before going to bed!\n    * Rubber threads help prevent damage to floors\n    * For children ages 2 years and up\n    * Requires: 4 x AA 1.5V batteries and 3 x AAA 1.5V batteries (not included)\n'),
(66, 2, 'Radio Control Car Carolina', 'The first fashion radio controlled car: dynamic, trendy and easy to drive both indoors and outdoor use. The car moves in four directions: forward, reverse, right & left. The remote control can be fitted onto the car when not in use and its antenna becomes a useful carry handle.', 0, 'Radio_Control_Car_Carolina', 'Radio Control Car Carolina', 'The first fashion radio controlled car: dynamic, trendy and easy to drive both indoors and outdoor u', 'Radio Control Car Carolina undefined', '    * Remote Control Car for children as young as 2 years old\n    * Attachable remote control with carrying handle\n    * Four large direction buttons for little hands\n    * Encourages creativity and improves coordination skills\n    * Requires: 6 x AA batteries (not included)'),
(67, 2, 'Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle', 'Chiccoâ€™s Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle is modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes. The remote control is shaped like a set of handlebars and moves the motorcycle in four directions. The Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle also features speed control and even authentic Ducati sounds. The Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle will help improve your childâ€™s handling skills and coordination.', 2, 'Radio_Control_Ducati_Motorcycle', 'Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle', 'Chiccoâ€™s Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle is modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbik', 'Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle undefined', '    * Modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes\n    * Remote control shaped like a set of handlebars\n    * Motorcycle moves in four directions\n    * Features speed control and authentic Ducati sounds\n    * Helps improve childrenâ€™s handling skills and coordination\n    * For children ages 2 years and up\n    * Requires: 6 x AA Batteries (not included)\n    * 27.145 MHz'),
(68, 2, 'Chicco Mini Sleeper Bed', 'The comfortable, easy to assemble Sleeper Bed features a side pocket and a simple open and folding system. The bed includes a blanket, mattress and a handy carry bag to store it in which can be used also as a baby carrier. The fabric is surface washable only. Check out more Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Stoller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller.', 2, 'Chicco_Mini_Sleeper_Bed', 'Chicco Mini Sleeper Bed', 'The comfortable, easy to assemble Sleeper Bed features a side pocket and a simple open and folding s', 'Chicco Mini Sleeper Bed undefined', '    *  Holds up to a 22" doll\n    * Includes blanket, mattress and carry bag/carrier\n    * Pretty pink fabric decorated with fairies and hearts\n    * Surface-washable fabric\n    * Matches all the Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Stroller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller\n    * Great for children ages 3 years and up\n'),
(69, 2, 'Chicco Mini Table Seat', 'A table seat for baby dolls to sit at the stable with you at meal time. It is easy to attach and remove from the table, just like real ones! The fabric cover is surface washable only. Check out more Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, the Mini Chicco Stoller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller.', 1, 'Chicco_Mini_Table_Seat', 'Chicco Mini Table Seat', 'A table seat for baby dolls to sit at the stable with you at meal time. It is easy to attach and rem', 'Chicco Mini Table Seat undefined', '    *  Holds up to a 22" doll\n    * Attaches to table like the real Chicco TravelSeat\n    * Pretty pink fabric decorated with fairies and hearts\n    * Surface-washable fabric\n    * Matches all the Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, the Mini Chicco Stroller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller\n    * Great for children ages 3 years and up\n'),
(70, 2, 'LEFT 4 DEAD 2', 'Left 4 Dead 2 is the sequel to the best-selling and critically-acclaimed co-operative multiplayer smash from Valve, creators of the Half-Life, Portal, Team Fortress and Counter-Strike game properties. Left 4 Dead 2 promises to become one of 2009''s top-selling games and set a new benchmark for co-operative action games. The title adds melee combat to the award-winning L4D style of play, with items such as a chainsaw, frying pan, axe, baseball bat, and more.\n\nIntroducing the AI Director 2.0, L4D''s dynamic gameplay is taken to the next level by giving the Director the ability to procedurally change weather effects, world objects, and pathways in addition to tailoring the enemy population, effects, and sounds to match the players'' performance. The result is a unique game session custom fitted to provide a satisfying and uniquely challenging experience each time the game is played.\n\nFinally, with new Survivors, boss zombies, weapons, and items, Lefct 4 Dead 2 offers a much larger game than the original with more co-operative campaigns, more Versus campaigns, maps for Survival mode at launch, and more.\n\nSupported by a $10+ million marketing campaign, Left 4 Dead has sold over 2.5 million retail copies since it was released in November of 2008. Left 4 Dead 2 is targeted for release on Xbox 360 and the PC this November, and will be launched worldwide with a multi-million dollar marketing campaign across TV, Outdoor and Online.\n\nLeft 4 Dead 2 is set at roughly the same time as the original â€“ just after the outbreak that turned most of the population into various zombie mutants. Players assume the role of 4 new â€œSurvivors,â€ each with their own personality and new dialog. The game leads these â€œSurvivorsâ€ through the southeastern region of the US - from Savannah, Georgia thru the bayou country, and climaxing in New Orleansâ€™ French Quarter.\n\n    * - Next generation co-op action gaming from the makers of Half-Life, Portal, Team Fortress and Counter-Strike.\n    * - AI Director 2.0: Advanced technology dubbed â€œThe AI Directorâ€ drove L4Dâ€™s unique gameplay â€“ customizing enemy population, effects, and music, based upon the playersâ€™ performance. L4D 2 features â€œThe AI Director 2.0â€ which expands the Directorâ€™s ability to customize level layout, world objects, weather, and lighting to reflect different times of day.\n    * - New melee weapons â€“ axe, chainsaw, frying pan, baseball bat â€“ allow you to get up close with the zombies\n    * - Four different survivors. New Story. New dialogue.\n    * - More game. On day one, L4D 2 features more co-operative campaigns, more campaigns and maps for the Versus game modes than L4D 1, plus support for Survival mode out of the box.\n    * - Stats, rankings, and awards system drives collaborative play\n', 3, 'LEFT_4_DEAD_2', 'LEFT 4 DEAD 2', 'Left 4 Dead 2 is the sequel to the best-selling and critically-acclaimed co-operative multiplayer sm', 'LEFT 4 DEAD 2 undefined', 'Left 4 Dead 2 is the sequel to the best-selling and critically-acclaimed co-operative multiplayer smash from Valve, creators of the Half-Life, Portal, Team Fortress and Counter-Strike game properties. Left 4 Dead 2 promises to become one of 2009''s top-selling games and set a new benchmark for co-operative action games. The title adds melee combat to the award-winning L4D style of play, with items such as a chainsaw, frying pan, axe, baseball bat, and more. '),
(71, 2, 'The Sims 3 World Adventures Expansion Pack', 'Take your Sims on the adventure of their lives with The Simsâ„¢ 3 World Adventures. Guide your Sims to acclaimed fortuneâ€”or potential doom. Take your Sims to exotic destinations to hunt for hidden treasures. Uncover new skills, experience new personality traits and garner rewards, if your Sims succeed. Explore ancient tombs in the pyramids of Egypt, master martial arts in the Far East, and discover rich culture and famous landmarks in France. Go online and for additional content and $10 worth of free SimPoints. Adventure is on the horizon â€” what will your Sims discover?\n\n    * Accept challenges, find treasures, discover whatâ€™s lurking in hidden caves and more.\n    * Explore famous landmarks in China, Egypt, and France.\n    * Learn new skills like photography and pursue new opportunities.\n    * Meet new Sims from exotic locations and share their cultures.\n    * Customize your Sims homes with new styles & artifacts from their adventures.\n    * Get $10 worth of free SimPoints for The Sims 3 Store as well as additional online features soon to be announced.\n', 2, 'The_Sims_3_World_Adventures_Expansion_Pack', 'The Sims 3 World Adventures Expansion Pack', 'Take your Sims on the adventure of their lives with The Simsâ„¢ 3 World Adventures. Guide your Sims to', 'The Sims 3 World Adventures Expansion Pack undefined', 'Take your Sims on the adventure of their lives with The Simsâ„¢ 3 World Adventures. Guide your Sims to acclaimed fortuneâ€”or potential doom. ');
