(62, 3, 'Ducati Grand Prix ', 'The Ducati Race Track features two mini remote-controlled bikes modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes. By grasping the infrared handle bar, your child can drive the mini Ducati bikes around the curves and over the bumps of the Grand Prix racetrack. The Ducati Race Track includes accessories like a start line, pit stop, crash barriers, and advertising boards and even features real Grand Prix Race Track sounds effects. Donâ€™t forget to check out Chiccoâ€™s Remote Control Ducati Motorcycles. ', 1, 'Ducati_Grand_Prix_', 'Ducati Grand Prix ', 'The Ducati Race Track features two mini remote-controlled bikes modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance', 'Ducati Grand Prix  undefined', '    * Features two mini remote-controlled Ducati motorcycles and a Grand Prix Race Track\n    * Motorcycles designed after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes\n    * Drive the bikes on or off the Grand Prix Racetrack\n    * Includes accessories like a start line, pit stop, crash barriers, and advertising boards\n    * For children ages 2 years and up\n    * Requires: 8 x AA batteries (not included)'),
(63, 3, 'Ct 0.5 Doll Stroller', 'Chiccoâ€™s Ct.5 Doll Stroller is a great accessory for your daughterâ€™s dolls. Designed just like Chiccoâ€™s Ct0.5 Stroller, this mini stroller is fully accessorized. It is easy to fold and has front swivel wheels, a reclining backrest, a storage basket, and a sun canopy. Check out more Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, and the Mini Chicco Pram. The Mini Chicco accessories are designed for children ages 3 and older.', 0, 'Ct_0.5_Doll_Stroller', 'Ct 0.5 Doll Stroller', 'Chiccoâ€™s Ct.5 Doll Stroller is a great accessory for your daughterâ€™s dolls. Designed just like Chicc', 'Ct 0.5 Doll Stroller undefined', '    *  Designed after the Chicco Ct0.5 Stroller\n    * Holds up to a 22" doll\n    * Fully accessorized: front swivel wheels, a reclining backrest, a storage basket, and a sun canopy\n    * Matches all the Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, and the Mini Chicco Pram\n    * For children ages 3 years and up\n'),
(64, 3, 'Radio Control ATV', 'The Radio Control ATV is a great introduction to the big kids world of remote control cars for your child as young as 2 years old. This brightly colored, smiling car comes with a remote control that attaches to the car and becomes the spare tire. The remote control comes with large buttons for little hands and controls the car in four directions. The Radio Control ATV will also improve your child''s coordination skills and will encourage creativity.', 4, 'Radio_Control_ATV', 'Radio Control ATV', 'The Radio Control ATV is a great introduction to the big kids world of remote control cars for your ', 'Radio Control ATV undefined', '    *  Remote Control Car for children as young as 2 years old\n    * Attachable remote control that becomes a spare tire\n    * Four large direction buttons for little hands\n    * Promotes creativity and improves coordination skills\n    * Requires: 4 x AA & 3 x AAA batteries (not included)'),
(65, 3, 'Billy Fun Wheels ', 'Make way for Billy Fun Wheels, the first motion-sensing remote control monster truck for children 2 years and up! The intuitive remote control is shaped just like a steering wheel, and rotating it makes the truck turn left or right. Arrows on the steering remote light up to help the child understand which way the truck will head. Engine sounds and working headlights add to the realism of  "driving" the truck, and a fun honk warns everybody that Billy is here! ', 2, 'Billy_Fun_Wheels_', 'Billy Fun Wheels ', 'Make way for Billy Fun Wheels, the first motion-sensing remote control monster truck for children 2 ', 'Billy Fun Wheels  undefined', '    *  The first motion-controlled monster truck for preschoolers!\n    * Intuitive steering wheel can be rotated left or right to steer the truck\n    * Realistic engine, reverse capability, and honking sounds add to the fun\n    * Headlights light up - all the better for those nighttime races before going to bed!\n    * Rubber threads help prevent damage to floors\n    * For children ages 2 years and up\n    * Requires: 4 x AA 1.5V batteries and 3 x AAA 1.5V batteries (not included)\n'),
(66, 3, 'Radio Control Car Carolina', 'The first fashion radio controlled car: dynamic, trendy and easy to drive both indoors and outdoor use. The car moves in four directions: forward, reverse, right & left. The remote control can be fitted onto the car when not in use and its antenna becomes a useful carry handle.', 0, 'Radio_Control_Car_Carolina', 'Radio Control Car Carolina', 'The first fashion radio controlled car: dynamic, trendy and easy to drive both indoors and outdoor u', 'Radio Control Car Carolina undefined', '    * Remote Control Car for children as young as 2 years old\n    * Attachable remote control with carrying handle\n    * Four large direction buttons for little hands\n    * Encourages creativity and improves coordination skills\n    * Requires: 6 x AA batteries (not included)'),
(67, 3, 'Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle', 'Chiccoâ€™s Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle is modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes. The remote control is shaped like a set of handlebars and moves the motorcycle in four directions. The Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle also features speed control and even authentic Ducati sounds. The Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle will help improve your childâ€™s handling skills and coordination.', 2, 'Radio_Control_Ducati_Motorcycle', 'Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle', 'Chiccoâ€™s Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle is modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbik', 'Radio Control Ducati Motorcycle undefined', '    * Modeled after Italyâ€™s Hi-Performance Ducati 999 Superbikes\n    * Remote control shaped like a set of handlebars\n    * Motorcycle moves in four directions\n    * Features speed control and authentic Ducati sounds\n    * Helps improve childrenâ€™s handling skills and coordination\n    * For children ages 2 years and up\n    * Requires: 6 x AA Batteries (not included)\n    * 27.145 MHz'),
(68, 3, 'Chicco Mini Sleeper Bed', 'The comfortable, easy to assemble Sleeper Bed features a side pocket and a simple open and folding system. The bed includes a blanket, mattress and a handy carry bag to store it in which can be used also as a baby carrier. The fabric is surface washable only. Check out more Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Stoller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller.', 2, 'Chicco_Mini_Sleeper_Bed', 'Chicco Mini Sleeper Bed', 'The comfortable, easy to assemble Sleeper Bed features a side pocket and a simple open and folding s', 'Chicco Mini Sleeper Bed undefined', '    *  Holds up to a 22" doll\n    * Includes blanket, mattress and carry bag/carrier\n    * Pretty pink fabric decorated with fairies and hearts\n    * Surface-washable fabric\n    * Matches all the Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Table Seat, the Mini Chicco Stroller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller\n    * Great for children ages 3 years and up\n'),
(69, 3, 'Chicco Mini Table Seat', 'A table seat for baby dolls to sit at the stable with you at meal time. It is easy to attach and remove from the table, just like real ones! The fabric cover is surface washable only. Check out more Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, the Mini Chicco Stoller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller.', 1, 'Chicco_Mini_Table_Seat', 'Chicco Mini Table Seat', 'A table seat for baby dolls to sit at the stable with you at meal time. It is easy to attach and rem', 'Chicco Mini Table Seat undefined', '    *  Holds up to a 22" doll\n    * Attaches to table like the real Chicco TravelSeat\n    * Pretty pink fabric decorated with fairies and hearts\n    * Surface-washable fabric\n    * Matches all the Mini Chicco accessories like the Chiccolini Flower Chics, the Mini Chicco Sleeper Bed, the Mini Chicco Stroller, the Mini Chicco Pram, and the Ct.5 Doll Stroller\n    * Great for children ages 3 years and up\n'),
(70, 3, 'LEFT 4 DEAD 2', 'Left 4 Dead 2 is the sequel to the best-selling and critically-acclaimed co-operative multiplayer smash from Valve, creators of the Half-Life, Portal, Team Fortress and Counter-Strike game properties. Left 4 Dead 2 promises to become one of 2009''s top-selling games and set a new benchmark for co-operative action games. The title adds melee combat to the award-winning L4D style of play, with items such as a chainsaw, frying pan, axe, baseball bat, and more.\n\nIntroducing the AI Director 2.0, L4D''s dynamic gameplay is taken to the next level by giving the Director the ability to procedurally change weather effects, world objects, and pathways in addition to tailoring the enemy population, effects, and sounds to match the players'' performance. The result is a unique game session custom fitted to provide a satisfying and uniquely challenging experience each time the game is played.\n\nFinally, with new Survivors, boss zombies, weapons, and items, Lefct 4 Dead 2 offers a much larger game than the original with more co-operative campaigns, more Versus campaigns, maps for Survival mode at launch, and more.\n\nSupported by a $10+ million marketing campaign, Left 4 Dead has sold over 2.5 million retail copies since it was released in November of 2008. Left 4 Dead 2 is targeted for release on Xbox 360 and the PC this November, and will be launched worldwide with a multi-million dollar marketing campaign across TV, Outdoor and Online.\n\nLeft 4 Dead 2 is set at roughly the same time as the original â€“ just after the outbreak that turned most of the population into various zombie mutants. Players assume the role of 4 new â€œSurvivors,â€ each with their own personality and new dialog. The game leads these â€œSurvivorsâ€ through the southeastern region of the US - from Savannah, Georgia thru the bayou country, and climaxing in New Orleansâ€™ French Quarter.\n\n    * - Next generation co-op action gaming from the makers of Half-Life, Portal, Team Fortress and Counter-Strike.\n    * - AI Director 2.0: Advanced technology dubbed â€œThe AI Directorâ€ drove L4Dâ€™s unique gameplay â€“ customizing enemy population, effects, and music, based upon the playersâ€™ performance. L4D 2 features â€œThe AI Director 2.0â€ which expands the Directorâ€™s ability to customize level layout, world objects, weather, and lighting to reflect different times of day.\n    * - New melee weapons â€“ axe, chainsaw, frying pan, baseball bat â€“ allow you to get up close with the zombies\n    * - Four different survivors. New Story. New dialogue.\n    * - More game. On day one, L4D 2 features more co-operative campaigns, more campaigns and maps for the Versus game modes than L4D 1, plus support for Survival mode out of the box.\n    * - Stats, rankings, and awards system drives collaborative play\n', 3, 'LEFT_4_DEAD_2', 'LEFT 4 DEAD 2', 'Left 4 Dead 2 is the sequel to the best-selling and critically-acclaimed co-operative multiplayer sm', 'LEFT 4 DEAD 2 undefined', 'Left 4 Dead 2 is the sequel to the best-selling and critically-acclaimed co-operative multiplayer smash from Valve, creators of the Half-Life, Portal, Team Fortress and Counter-Strike game properties. Left 4 Dead 2 promises to become one of 2009''s top-selling games and set a new benchmark for co-operative action games. The title adds melee combat to the award-winning L4D style of play, with items such as a chainsaw, frying pan, axe, baseball bat, and more. '),
(71, 3, 'The Sims 3 World Adventures Expansion Pack', 'Take your Sims on the adventure of their lives with The Simsâ„¢ 3 World Adventures. Guide your Sims to acclaimed fortuneâ€”or potential doom. Take your Sims to exotic destinations to hunt for hidden treasures. Uncover new skills, experience new personality traits and garner rewards, if your Sims succeed. Explore ancient tombs in the pyramids of Egypt, master martial arts in the Far East, and discover rich culture and famous landmarks in France. Go online and for additional content and $10 worth of free SimPoints. Adventure is on the horizon â€” what will your Sims discover?\n\n    * Accept challenges, find treasures, discover whatâ€™s lurking in hidden caves and more.\n    * Explore famous landmarks in China, Egypt, and France.\n    * Learn new skills like photography and pursue new opportunities.\n    * Meet new Sims from exotic locations and share their cultures.\n    * Customize your Sims homes with new styles & artifacts from their adventures.\n    * Get $10 worth of free SimPoints for The Sims 3 Store as well as additional online features soon to be announced.\n', 2, 'The_Sims_3_World_Adventures_Expansion_Pack', 'The Sims 3 World Adventures Expansion Pack', 'Take your Sims on the adventure of their lives with The Simsâ„¢ 3 World Adventures. Guide your Sims to', 'The Sims 3 World Adventures Expansion Pack undefined', 'Take your Sims on the adventure of their lives with The Simsâ„¢ 3 World Adventures. Guide your Sims to acclaimed fortuneâ€”or potential doom. ');
